{"tid":2272270,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【跪求幫推】萬一拜登選贏嘅Contingency Plan","createTime":"2020-11-05T03:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T11:48:06.000Z","uid":90735,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1d02a958ff63010cbc00acbe088e8768c7180384","tid":2272270,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:29:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">萬一拜登選贏，請求侵侵兩個月內，為咗美國人民嘅日後幸福做以下三樣嘢：</span></strong><br />\n1. 追求武肺責任<br />\n2. 強硬對付邪惡帝国<br />\n3. 盡快出售武器俾太平洋盟友<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">方法：</span></strong><br />\n1. 寫email俾共和黨人<br />\n2. Twitter<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">心態：</span></strong><br />\n1. 要強調「為咗美國人民嘅日後幸福」而做<br />\n2. 國際線兩手準備，唔好屌票、唔好屌拜登、唔好屌拜登支持者，<span class=\"red\">改變策略</span><br />\n<blockquote>打開國際戰線 其實侵真係輸咗都唔駛太灰 - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2272163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2272163</a><br />\n當拜登真正上台就要改<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">要由攻擊_共嘅共產主義同_國人劣根性</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"green\">改為攻擊_共嘅帝國主義 反人權反人性同種族主義入手</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">貼多啲城管趕黑人落街 貼多啲小粉紅歧視人<br />\n宣傳_共係法西斯多過共產 唔好打中左派個G點<br />\n支持同性戀同小數族群手足</span></blockquote><br />\n3. <span class=\"red\">萬一拜登選贏係最終結果，屌票都冇用</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>走難/移民嘅請參考呢個post互相幫忙、繼續抗爭</strong></span><br />\n【BNO/走難撚入】香港方舟聯盟城市，將全球出現 - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2120221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2120221</a><br />\n移民驚無嘢做？<span class=\"red\">年輕嘅你不妨爭取加入英軍</span>"},{"pid":"36d04209fbb1e5dda9d3ff719dbeac881e753378","tid":2272270,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:30:40.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d565b4e819ed4eee06e6ada4df458895b30218ea","tid":2272270,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime